            "tab_1_heading": "Description",
            "tab_1_content_type": "text",
            "tab_1_text": "<p>TrueFit is a clean, all-in-one protein built to power weight loss, muscle gain, and better daily nutrition. Every scoop combines 25g of grass-fed whey with fiber, prebiotics and probiotics to support smooth digestion, fight bloating, and help your body actually use the protein you’re taking in. Its balanced macros keep you full for hours, curb cravings, and make staying on track feel effortless. With thoughtfully sourced ingredients and zero unnecessary junk, TrueFit delivers big results—fueling strength, recovery, and feel-good performance day after day.</p>",
