            "tab_3_text": "<p>Add 1 scoop of TrueFit to 8–12 oz of cold milk or your favorite non-dairy altnerative (almond, oat, coconut - go wild). Shake or blend until smooth and creamy. Water works in a pinch… but if you want that rich, milkshake vibe? Milk (or alt milk) is the move.</p>",
